            <p rend="indent(1)">Present</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">I take pleasure<lb/> in informing you that I have<lb/> secured to
                your valuable weekly<lb/> a subscriber. His name and<lb/> address is: <persName>P.
                    Morris</persName>. <placeName>Crawfordsville,<lb/> Georgia</placeName>. Please
                advertise in your<lb/> next edition the receipt of the<lb/> yearly subscription, and
                call upon<lb/> me for the money.<lb/> Yours very Truly</p>
